There are copies
available in the back.

00:38:31.001 --> 00:38:32.750
BRYAN SMITH: Makes a
great Christmas gift.

00:38:32.750 --> 00:38:33.070
DAVE LANGERT: Yep.

00:38:33.070 --> 00:38:35.737
And it's also available on
Amazon and other bookstores.

00:38:35.737 --> 00:38:37.020
BRYAN SMITH: Yes, indeed.

00:38:37.020 --> 00:38:37.560
DAVE LANGERT: Thank you.

00:38:37.560 --> 00:38:38.190
BRYAN SMITH: Thank you.

00:38:38.190 --> 00:38:38.923
